        <div style={{background:C.redBg,borderRadius:12,padding:"13px 15px",marginBottom:14,border:`1px solid ${C.red}44`}}><div style={{fontSize:14,fontWeight:700,color:C.red,marginBottom:3}}>Safety check — {safetyCrewRoute.name}</div><div style={{fontSize:12,color:C.textSub,lineHeight:1.6}}>Backcountry objective. Align on risk and turnaround, synthesize gear, and file a float plan with your crew before you commit.</div></div>
